{"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"int","preciseIdentifier":"c:I"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"samSelectDetailRegion"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"keyword","text":"const"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/DotFaceCore\/documentation\/DotFaceCore\/sam_color_image","text":"SamColorImage","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:@S@sam_color_image"},{"text":" * ","kind":"text"},{"text":"image","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"text":"const","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"int","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:I"},{"text":" * ","kind":"text"},{"text":"detectedObjectBoundingBox","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"text":"int","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:I"},{"text":" * ","kind":"text"},{"text":"selectedBoundingBox","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":");","kind":"text"}],"platforms":["iOS"],"languages":["occ"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"content":[{"type":"heading","anchor":"return-value","text":"Return Value","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"0 on success, or a non-zero error code on failure.","type":"text"}]}],"kind":"content"},{"content":[{"type":"heading","anchor":"discussion","text":"Discussion","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Analyzes the input image and identifies the most suitable 200x200 pixel","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"region (bounding box) with high level of details that intersects a given bounding box.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"If ","type":"text"},{"code":"detectedObjectBoundingBox","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" is empty (width or height is 0), any region can be selected. Otherwise,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the selected region should have non-empty intersection with this bounding box. The selected region","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"should lie fully inside the input image.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"If there is no region satisfying these conditions - if image width or height is smaller than 200","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"or ","type":"text"},{"code":"detectedObjectBoundingBox","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" lies outside the image, the selected bounding box will be (0, 0, 200, 200).","type":"text"}]},{"type":"codeListing","code":["                                  a bounding box in the format (x, y, width, height)."],"syntax":null},{"type":"codeListing","code":["                                  return, contains the bounding box in the format (x, y, width, height),","                                  where width and height are always set to 200."],"syntax":null}],"kind":"content"}],"sections":[],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/dotfacecore\/samselectdetailregion"]}],"kind":"symbol","hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/DotFaceCore\/documentation\/DotFaceCore"]]},"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"metadata":{"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"samSelectDetailRegion"}],"role":"symbol","symbolKind":"func","externalID":"c:@F@samSelectDetailRegion","fragments":[{"text":"samSelectDetailRegion","kind":"identifier"}],"roleHeading":"Function","modules":[{"name":"DotFaceCore"}],"title":"samSelectDetailRegion"},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/DotFaceCore\/documentation\/DotFaceCore\/samSelectDetailRegion","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"references":{"doc://DotFaceCore/documentation/DotFaceCore":{"type":"topic","abstract":[{"text":"version: 9.2.2","type":"text"}],"title":"DotFaceCore","kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/DotFaceCore\/documentation\/DotFaceCore","role":"collection","url":"\/documentation\/dotfacecore"},"doc://DotFaceCore/documentation/DotFaceCore/samSelectDetailRegion":{"kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"samSelectDetailRegion","